Acknowledgments

This project is a clean-room reimplementation of a TMF8829 host driver. The
public protocol semantics, register layout, command opcodes, and bootloader
sequence were learned from the reference drivers published by ams-OSRAM AG
under the MIT license:

  Copyright (c) 2024-2025 ams-OSRAM AG
  - "tmf8829 arduino driver"
  - "tmf8829 linux driver"
  Both released under the MIT License (and the linux driver additionally
  under GPL-2.0-or-later).

The optional default firmware image shipped under image/ is the unmodified
binary produced by ams-OSRAM AG and is redistributed under the same MIT
license terms as the original ams-OSRAM tmf8829 reference drivers.
